CHANGES
    Here's what's new in version 6.000 of Dist-Zilla-PluginBundle-Author-CJM:
    (See the file "Changes" for the full revision history.)

	- Change major version to 6, because Dist::Zilla 6 is required
	- Require ArchiveRelease 6 for Dist::Zilla 6



